{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the-- our family, so three children, and father, and mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I attended to the King Matthias High School, which was very near to the royal castle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's where I went for eight-- eight long years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after high school, I couldn't get to university, being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I studied quite a few things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my-- my favorite to study was acc-- account-- bookkeeping and accounting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got a job as a junior accountant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I still had the job when the Germans marched in, in the 19th of March, 1944.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just like to-- sorry-- mention one other thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the high school years, you might wish to hear that each time we had a religious class, they-- the Jewish teacher would came, or rabbi would came.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- and the headmaster would shout that, 'All stinking Jews out from the class.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your-- your rabbi is here.' So then all the Jews had to get up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were about-- there was about 13 Jews from a class of 40 or 50.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then all the Christians would shout, 'Ah, the stinking Jews are going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The air is getting much better now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wish you would never come back.' And-- and you know, they were throwing missiles at us and kicking us in the back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we-- we moved out and we went to the religious-- religious classes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was just a background atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyhow, it was a Sunday, 19th of March, 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a beautiful spring weather.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went with some of my friends to a Beethoven concert.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was-- life was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Already we knew that war can't go on much longer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Russians were advancing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were near the Hungarian border.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
